{"tid":453562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支付寶HK街市實測算順暢","createTime":"2017-10-31T09:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T08:44:27.000Z","uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"307e65c115b6ace0cd89a8ac5db75efd58b44cd8","tid":453562,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T09:50:03.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】「支付寶HK」早前殺入秀茂坪的寶達街市，以QR Code（二維碼）技術推「無現金街市」，記者上周到場實測，過程尚算順暢，但實際用戶並不多，生果檔員工指「每日都有十幾單。」<br />\n記者先後到生果檔、菜檔、燒味檔及小食店測試支付寶HK，生果檔職員明顯經過訓練，提起支付寶就「自動波」指示記者用手機掃瞄相關的QR Code，掃過後再輸入金額及密碼。其後去到菜檔買入5元3束的蕃薯葉，手機掃QR Code的反應快，惟每次交易亦都要輸入密碼，速度上比起直接掏出一個5元要慢得多。而燒味檔主就指，用現金找續難免會沾上手上油漬，用支付寶可以解決這個問題，惟支付寶機「有時load好耐都load唔到。」<br />\n推現金優惠吸客<br />\n<br />\n支付寶港澳區總經理李詠詩接受本報專訪時表示，香港電子支付上的最大挑戰是來自信用卡，但其門檻始終較高，現時仍有多於一半的商戶只收現金，特別是中小型商戶，故未來將會着力向他們埋手，街市正是其中之一。至於收費，她稱一定較信用卡公司為低，交易金額每日轉入商戶的銀行戶口。<br />\n被問到要如何教會家庭主婦用支付寶，她表示離不開優惠兩個字，新用戶在寶達街市可獲高達65元現金優惠，其他新用戶亦有50元的「新人禮包」，而方向上第一步始終會向年輕一輩，即20至40歲的年齡層埋手。<span style=\"color: red;\">她指，雖然年輕人對中資可能有偏見，但相信「如果幫到佢哋就會用，正如好多人都會喺淘寶買嘢。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171031/large/31bl25p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171031%2Flarge%2F31bl25p.jpg&h=bfd72823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171031/20199897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171031%2F20199897&d=KtABMy4PDxV5QEjRwU8ECzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f9509090\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171031%2F20199897&h=d948e439\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171031/20199897</a>"},{"pid":"a9c471bfa59ed1fa480d060e986434f50de5f17c","tid":453562,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"幫到d咩"},{"pid":"41b09c642addf4d8b7ab1be12b653b90f74bb0f6","tid":453562,"uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫到d咩</blockquote><br />\n減$5"},{"pid":"aa2f358e5426f30d68ec481f7358f979c4e11651","tid":453562,"uid":41818,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:16:29.000Z","msg":"&gt;惟每次交易亦都要輸入密碼，速度上比起直接掏出一個5元要慢得多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18586c016058b432cd4627dea5fd5c8b9e07808","tid":453562,"uid":35014,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ff3bbfc3b78a3f774cc66b484b5aadfe36840de","tid":453562,"uid":154106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T20:18:33.000Z","msg":"我一定唔會幫呀媽裝"},{"pid":"8721832837aa68826c2e261b4c7ce750f8c51e11","tid":453562,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T20:28:55.000Z","msg":"買棵菜都咁多步驟，不了"},{"pid":"4dcb540f7d34d4ca09d4562622ae935f5f6ef619","tid":453562,"uid":49955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T20:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一定唔會幫呀媽裝</blockquote><br />\n我一定會幫呀媽鏟"},{"pid":"96cb5330b003b3acf046774a31dc4e691d787380","tid":453562,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T20:30:45.000Z","msg":"街市啲錢銀好撚污糟<br />\n支那寶應該都好快掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de174d19065f906424ee98aa79b76f6aefdd983d","tid":453562,"uid":26266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T20:30:59.000Z","msg":"紅字啱呀，講中哂班港豬心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd27188cad7ce0eb90ceab12eb3675f5009d7ac","tid":453562,"uid":22858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T22:17:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛至愛</span></strong> <img src=\"/ass